sql:
SELECT SUM(quantity) AS total_quantity
FROM inventory_items
WHERE item_id = 123;

SELECT COUNT(dealer_id) AS dealer_count
FROM dealers
WHERE state = 'CA';

SELECT dealer_name
FROM dealers
ORDER BY dealer_name;

external_knowledge:
- Top 3 dealers refers to the 3 dealers with the highest total order cost over the last year; 
- "last year" means from the current date to one year ago; 
- Total order cost is the sum of the costs of all orders for a dealer.

sql:
SELECT COUNT(*) AS dealer_count
FROM dealers
